description: An Apple Newton is a personal digital assistant (PDA) first introduced in 1993.  Eight different models were produced before it was discontinued in 1998.  It was so advanced for its time that in 2012, most modern smartphones/pdas have yet to surpass it for usability and battery life.  This blog records my Apple Newton experiences, as well as comparisons with other PDAs, Smartphones and Mobile Devices.  It is also a repository for storing complex set up procedures for future reference.
title: My Apple Newton
